{"tid":833873,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Tiger Woods 終於贏到復出後首個冠軍","createTime":"2018-09-23T23:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T00:03:28.000Z","uid":130105,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c2c9af622ab0d56d62e828f721282153b18776b","tid":833873,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T23:01:25.000Z","msg":"18 洞個個場境，真係有今生冇來世 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&bull;Tiger Woods has won the Tour Championship to claim his first victory in five years and his 80th on PGA Tour <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/23/23/50979F2700000578-6199219-Tiger_Woods_has_gone_from_not_knowing_if_he_would_ever_play_golf-a-11_1537741236697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F50979F2700000578-6199219-Tiger_Woods_has_gone_from_not_knowing_if_he_would_ever_play_golf-a-11_1537741236697.jpg&h=c34ad5b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Tiger Woods has gone from not knowing if he would ever play golf again to winning a big tournament<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/23/23/50979E7F00000578-6199219-Woods_reacts_to_winning_the_tournament_on_Sunday_a_remarkable_co-a-9_1537741236688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F50979E7F00000578-6199219-Woods_reacts_to_winning_the_tournament_on_Sunday_a_remarkable_co-a-9_1537741236688.jpg&h=a2a35072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Woods reacts to winning the tournament on Sunday - a remarkable comeback that thrilled golf fans eager to see the old Tiger<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1/2018/09/23/23/4501304-6199219-Tiger_Woods_claimed_victory_at_the_Tour_Championship_at_East_Lak-a-12_1537741352064.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F4501304-6199219-Tiger_Woods_claimed_victory_at_the_Tour_Championship_at_East_Lak-a-12_1537741352064.jpg&h=6294d252&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The gallery at East Lake was enormous in anticipation of Woods winning for the first time in more than five years <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/23/23/5097B06C00000578-6199219-image-a-25_1537742166080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F5097B06C00000578-6199219-image-a-25_1537742166080.jpg&h=6e5c219c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Woods' imminent victory sent a buzz throughout the crowd in the gallery which followed him to the final hole<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/23/23/5097B04500000578-6199219-image-a-28_1537742197519.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F5097B04500000578-6199219-image-a-28_1537742197519.jpg&h=41b51463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Woods led throughout the final round and finished at 11-under-par 269 at East Lake, where he carded a closing 71 for his 80th PGA Tour victory<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/23/23/5097B02F00000578-6199219-image-a-30_1537742236692.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F5097B02F00000578-6199219-image-a-30_1537742236692.jpg&h=6173b0b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The aerial shot at East Lake just before the final hole shows the gallery wait in anticipation of Woods' victory<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/23/23/5097AF3200000578-6199219-image-a-32_1537742848558.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F5097AF3200000578-6199219-image-a-32_1537742848558.jpg&h=64c21d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Woods' performance at East Lake will only boost expectations for the upcoming Ryder Cup tournament<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/23/23/50966D7000000578-6199219-Tiger_Woods_who_not_long_ago_wasn_t_sure_if_he_would_ever_play_g-a-5_1537741236563.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F50966D7000000578-6199219-Tiger_Woods_who_not_long_ago_wasn_t_sure_if_he_would_ever_play_g-a-5_1537741236563.jpg&h=59a1e978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Tiger Woods, who not long ago wasn't sure if he would ever play golf again, captured the PGA Tour Championship on Sunday<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/23/23/5096743D00000578-6199219-Woods_foreground_approaches_the_ninth_hole_during_the_final_roun-a-6_1537741236580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F5096743D00000578-6199219-Woods_foreground_approaches_the_ninth_hole_during_the_final_roun-a-6_1537741236580.jpg&h=04305ec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Woods, foreground, approaches the ninth hole during the final round of the Tour Championship in Atlanta<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1/2018/09/23/23/4500902-6199219-Woods_claimed_victory_at_the_Tour_Championship_at_East_Lake_on_S-a-8_1537741236621.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F4500902-6199219-Woods_claimed_victory_at_the_Tour_Championship_at_East_Lake_on_S-a-8_1537741236621.jpg&h=910ee600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Woods claimed victory at the Tour Championship at East Lake on Sunday to win his first title in five years<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1/2018/09/23/23/4500908-6199219-It_was_the_80th_title_Woods_has_won_on_the_PGA_Tour_after_a_sens-a-7_1537741236619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F4500908-6199219-It_was_the_80th_title_Woods_has_won_on_the_PGA_Tour_after_a_sens-a-7_1537741236619.jpg&h=01c7519b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n It was the 80th title Woods has won on the PGA Tour after a sensational weekend at the challenging course in Atlanta<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1/2018/09/23/23/4500916-6199219-The_former_world_No_1_and_14_time_major_champion_his_top_form_ov-a-13_1537741434234.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F4500916-6199219-The_former_world_No_1_and_14_time_major_champion_his_top_form_ov-a-13_1537741434234.jpg&h=b51654f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The former world No 1 and 14-time major champion his top form over the weekend and never contemplated looking back<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1/2018/09/23/23/4500910-6199219-Woods_round_wasn_t_without_his_problems_but_he_was_able_to_maint-a-14_1537741438341.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F4500910-6199219-Woods_round_wasn_t_without_his_problems_but_he_was_able_to_maint-a-14_1537741438341.jpg&h=109a262f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Woods' round wasn't without his problems but he was able to maintain a high standard and see out a deserved win<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/23/23/5097ACFF00000578-6199219-image-a-16_1537741627419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F23%2F23%2F5097ACFF00000578-6199219-image-a-16_1537741627419.jpg&h=1b9beada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Woods has come a long way since his May 2017 arrest for driving under the influence. He is seen above being arrested by Palm Beach County Sheriff's deputies in Florida<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6199219/Tiger-Woods-verge-capping-comeback-win.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-6199219%2FTiger-Woods-verge-capping-comeback-win.html&d=wPtz1vOvgA63T78xIRbl4LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=41a7feb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6199219/Tiger-Woods-verge-capping-comeback-win.html</a>"},{"pid":"7889be0417378f784947f0be9d41e3e330ae8148","tid":833873,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T23:53:55.000Z","msg":"可惜rose第18洞birdie岩岩好贏左Fedex Cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89334e8eb0619fb6fbfbd9c5ee6a4b1b0cb6be29","tid":833873,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7889be0417378f784947f0be9d41e3e330ae8148","tid":833873,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T23:53:55.000Z","msg":"可惜rose第18洞birdie岩岩好贏左Fedex Cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T23:58:22.000Z","msg":"係，袋咗十球都冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248fac1eee82e66bf65d7dec8680d407a8697f16","tid":833873,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89334e8eb0619fb6fbfbd9c5ee6a4b1b0cb6be29","tid":833873,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7889be0417378f784947f0be9d41e3e330ae8148","tid":833873,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T23:53:55.000Z","msg":"可惜rose第18洞birdie岩岩好贏左Fedex Cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T23:58:22.000Z","msg":"係，袋咗十球都冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T00:03:28.000Z","msg":"真正贏家冇人理<img sr